data.description: All spruced up, passed occupancy and ready for new homeowners!  This 4-bedroom home in Godfrey township has so much to offer for a family looking to grow -- 4 bedrooms, both family and living rooms, 2-car spacious garage, fenced yard for kids and pets, tons of storage space and a great neighborhood with easy access to schools and major highways.  Primary bedroom is extra large with 2 closets; lower level has 2 bedrooms, a family room and a full bath with new exhaust fan. Gazebo out back is wired and ready for party lights and music. New dishwasher. Sump pump in laundry room; drainage line across the back yard ties into the municipal sewer drain to eliminate standing water. Before making an offer on any property, buyer should independently verify all MLS data, which is derived from various sources and not warranted as accurate.
